Data templates are similar to app templates, but contain assets such as data connectors, recipes, and datasets. For limits and limitations, see Data Pipelines Limits and Limitations.

Data template features:

TEMPLATE FEATURE	APP TEMPLATE	DATA TEMPLATE
Data sync			100 mb/day	10 gb/day
Visualization assets: lens and dashboards			
Data assets: recipes and datasets		
Template Rules Engine		
Monitor and troubleshoot templated app creation		

For more information, see the Analytics Template Developer Guide.
